						<summary>

						<p>Built in. Registers a gift of 40 <hi rend="italic">kaḻañju</hi> for several offerings to the god. The record belongs to <hi rend="bold">Kōvirāja-Rājakēsari</hi> i.e. <hi rend="bold">Rājarāja I.</hi> Another fragment below this contains part of the <hi rend="italic">praśasti</hi> of Rājēndrachōḷa I.</p>						

