<div type="edition" xml:lang="tam-Latn" rendition="class:tamil maturity:vernacular">

<p>
<lb n="1"/>ṭe ceḻiyarait tecu koḷ <hi rend="grantha">śrī</hi> kovirā<hi rend="grantha">ja</hi>rā<hi rend="grantha">ja</hi>ke
<lb n="2"/>l poṉ <num value="40">4 <g type="numeral">10</g></num>rūpāy pon nāṟpatin kaḻañcuṉāl kaḻañciṉ vāttiṅ
<lb n="3"/>ṉāl poṉ rūpāy vāḻaippaḻam <num value="300">3 <g type="numeral">100</g></num> ṉāl poṉ kū <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> cū
<lb n="4"/>celuttuvippommāṉom tiruvaraṅkattu <hi rend="grantha">sabhai</hi>yom 
</p>

<p>Another fragment in similar characters reads as follows:—</p>

<p>
<lb n="1"/>ṇṭicai pukaḻtara yiḻamaṇṭalamun tiṇṭiṟal ve
<lb n="2"/>tu ceytaruḷavum cārttiyaruḷun tirupariyica
</p>

